is work is to discover these unwritten rules and norms behind Arabic letter writing on papyrus.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aArabic lettersxHistory and criticism. 0aLetter writing, ArabicxHistory. 0aManuscripts, Arabic (Papyri). 4aArabisch. 4aArabistik. 4aEpistolographie. 4aPapyrologie. 4aUrkundenlehre. 4aÄgypten. 7aHISTORY / Middle East / General.2bisacsh  aArabic letters.  aArabisation.  aEpistolography.  aIslamisation.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA History 2000 - 2014z9783110635836oZDB-23-GHI08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2010z9783110233544oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE ENGLISH LANGUAGES TITLES 2010z978311023355108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET ALTERTUM 2010z9783110233575oZDB-23-DGD0 cprintz978311024704640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311024705340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110247053423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110247053/original  a978-3-11-023355-1  E-BOOK PACKAGE ENGLISH LANGUAGES TITLES 2010b2010  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1c2000d2014  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_CL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGDb2010  aZDB-23-DGGb2010  aZDB-23-GHIc2000d2014